-----------------------------------------------------------
    Reification
-----------------------------------------------------------
- transform a constraint into a 0/1 variable
	- 1 if constraint satistifed

-----------------------------------------------------------
    Element Constraint
-----------------------------------------------------------
- ability to index an array/matrix with a variable/expression with variables
- c is an array of Integers
- x, y variables
- x = c[y]

-----------------------------------------------------------
    Global constraints
-----------------------------------------------------------
- captures combinatorial substructures
- allows exploitation with dedicated algorithm
- discovers infeasibility earlier
- allows more aggressive pruning
eg. alldifferent(x1..xn)
	- instead of creating pairwise not equal constraint, can have one alldiff
eg. table constraint
	- enumerate what are feasible combinations
	- specify subset of cartesian product